title: Khalid Eisa
summary: Khalid Eisa Mohammed Bilal Saeed Al Mesmari (Arabic: خَالِد عِيْسى مُحَمَّد بِلَال سَعِيْد الْمِسْمَارِيّ; born 15 September 1989) is an Emirati professional association football goalkeeper who plays for Emirati club Al Ain and the United Arab Emirates national team. He competed at the 2012 Summer Olympics and the 2018 FIFA Club World Cup.
